{
  "rules": {
    "config": {
      ".read": true,
      ".write": false
    },
    "users": {
      "$userId": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true
      }
    },
    "analytics": {
      "$path": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true
      }
    },
    "usage": {
      "$userId": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true
      }
    },
    "sessions": {
      "$sessionId": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true
      }
    },
    "payments": {
      "$paymentId": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true
      }
    }
  }
}

/* 
Firebase Console mein yeh steps follow karo:

1. https://console.firebase.google.com/ pe jao
2. Apna project select karo (linked-in-recruiter-pro)
3. Left menu mein "Realtime Database" click karo
4. "Rules" tab click karo
5. Upar wala JSON copy-paste karo
6. "Publish" button click karo

Yeh rules allow karenge:
- config: READ only (admin settings)
- users: READ/WRITE (user data)  
- analytics: READ/WRITE (usage tracking)
- usage: READ/WRITE (usage stats)
- sessions: READ/WRITE (session data)
- payments: READ/WRITE (payment records)
*/